{"article_id":"V4JvH6FmyOJEgaPg","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Obama said Friday","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"he hopes","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"that President-elect Donald Trump starts to show appropriate concern about allegations of Russian hacking into the U.S. election system ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"complaining","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that many Republicans were more worried about defeating Hillary Clinton","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"than they were about Moscow ' s alleged meddling in the election .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"\" My hope is that the president-elect is going to similarly be concerned with making sure","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that we don ' t have foreign influence in our election process , \"","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Mr. Obama said at his year-end press conference at the White House .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"\" That shouldn ' t be the source of an argument . \"","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Asked if he believes","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Russian President Vladimir Putin tried to help Mr. Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"the president said ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"\" Not much happens in Russia","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"without Vladimir Putin. \"","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"the intelligence reports","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"he ' s seen","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"give him \" great confidence \" in the assessment of the CIA and the FBI","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that Russia carried out the hacking .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Mr. Obama also blasted Republican officials , and GOP voters ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"for expressing positive views of Mr. Putin ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"noting","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that a recent poll found","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"that 37 percent of Republican voters approve of the former head of the KGB .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Mr. Trump has called Mr. Putin a strong leader .","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"\" Ronald Reagan would roll over in his grave , \"","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Mr. Obama said .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"The president blamed partisan divides in Washington ,","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"the GOP was more interested in hurting Democrats","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"than taking a stand against the autocratic Russian leader .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"\" Unless that changes ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"we ' re going to continue to be vulnerable to foreign influence , \"","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"The White House has grown increasingly hostile to Mr. Trump and his team","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"for rejecting the administration ' s argument","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"that Russia hacked into Democratic officials ' emails","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"and leaked them","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"in an effort","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"to help defeat Hillary Clinton .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"The Trump team has called on the White House to tone down its rhetoric for the good of the nation .","depth":4},{"id":42,"text":"Mr. Obama said","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"there ' s no doubt","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"that Russia is responsible for the hacking ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"and that he told Mr. Putin to \" cut it out \"","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"when he met him in China in September .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"there will be \" consequences \" for the cyberattacks ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"that the U.S. response would increase the \" costs \" to Russia of future cyberattacks .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"The president said","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"the U.S. retaliation for Russia ' s action must be carried out in a \" thoughtful , methodical way . \"","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"\" Some of it we will do in a way","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"that they know ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"but not everybody will , \"","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Mr. Obama also chided journalists","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"for publishing news stories","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"based on the stolen Democratic documents .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Sen. Ben Sasse , Nebraska Republican , said","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"the U.S. needs a more robust response to Russia .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"\" Blaming journalists for coverage and mere scolding of dictators for cyberattacks isn ' t a winning strategy , \"","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Mr. Sasse said .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"\" Instead of President Obama ' s vague ' we can do stuff , '","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Congress should debate upending Putin ' s calculus with a full menu of diplomatic , economic , military , and cyber responses .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"This isn ' t new :","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"China ' s OPM hack and Russia ' s aggressions make it clear","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"our adversaries think","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"these attacks are low-cost , high-reward gambles . \"","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"Asked if he believes","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Mrs. Clinton lost the election","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"because of Russian meddling ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"the president declined to answer directly .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"He did say","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"she was treated fairly during the election .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"the [ media ] coverage of her and the issues was troubling . \"","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Mr. Obama said","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"the issue of Russian hacking has been \" caught up in the carryover from election season. \"","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"But he said","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"he will still insist on a smooth transition","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"to help Mr. Trump ' s team take over power .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"they would be the first","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"to acknowledge","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"that we have done everything","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"we can , \"","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"Mr. Obama said .","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"\" That cooperation is going to continue . \"","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"The news conference was interrupted for several minutes","depth":3},{"id":92,"text":"when a journalist in the crowded press briefing room fainted .","depth":3},{"id":93,"text":"Mr. Obama stood at the podium","depth":4},{"id":94,"text":"and asked for staff to bring a doctor .","depth":4},{"id":95,"text":"Other journalists eventually helped the woman out a door ,","depth":4},{"id":96,"text":"where she was greeted by a White House physician","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"who had been summoned .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":195,"left":188,"right":194,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":188,"left":132,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":122,"right":131,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":122,"left":107,"right":121,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":103,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":100,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":0,"right":99,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":3,"right":101,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":105,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":104,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":121,"left":116,"right":120,"